In a message dated 6/11/03 12:29:27 AM Central Daylight Time, 
foxmanroar1@... writes:


> Scourge looked up at AzureBlade.... a blood lust began wailing up in him, 
> he felt his missile pods opening slowly, and all four arming.... then he saw 
> Maxima... and he became calm once more... He stood up and looked at his 
> injuries... He felt his mind pulling three different ways, his love of peace, his 
> thirst for war, and the unending rage and madness that was slowly begining to 
> wail up in his spark... The spark began again and his body jumped to life. 
> "Maxima... Somethings wrong..." His eyes began glowing red and he looked at the 
> two as the spark within him began to glow white hot... 
> 

She only gazed at him. As though she didn't care. But actually, she did. 
Whatever was happening to him, was possibly good. She waited... watching. 

Then indicated to the lagoon, "In. Bath in it's energy. & Reform!" 

--part1_34.3afcdb36.2c181a22_boundary
